roup, BB there are now people camping these gobbos, as they are great exp for their levels, and Unrest in which you can ask people to kill em for you. Unrest is the most dangerous, everything else is simple. and badda boom, with a lot of help and some ports, you have a Ghoulbane at level 10. Simple, just too Simple.....Just my output on this quest, though nicely done, is screwing up the market for Paladin Weapons. Pleae be welcome to post what you think on this topic too, i look forward to your responses.<br><br>Zomor Soulsaver-Champion of Brell, 46th Season<br>"Thunder is impressive, but Lightning gets the job done"</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >6 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
